Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.99,0:29:18.09,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.63,0:29:23.23,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}啊，稍微有點亂
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.24,0:29:24.32,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}請不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.24,0:29:29.03,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}這也叫…「稍微」？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.11,0:29:32.32,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}啊！抱歉，幫我把吃的放進冰箱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.88,0:29:33.72,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}…好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.06,0:29:35.65,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}冰塊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.69,0:29:37.57,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}零食
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.65,0:29:39.84,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}全是啤酒…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.87,0:29:42.52,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}過著什麼樣的生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.17,0:29:46.14,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}我要開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.15,0:29:47.24,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.42,0:29:55.46,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}COOL～
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.92,0:29:59.85,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}人生果然是為了這種時候而存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.75,0:30:04.34,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}不吃嗎？味道蠻不錯的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.34,0:30:05.43,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}雖然只是冷凍速食
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.25,0:30:07.50,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}不…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.88,0:30:10.03,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}我不太習慣這樣的晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.03,0:30:13.03,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}不行哦！挑食可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.41,0:30:15.35,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}不…我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.40,0:30:17.35,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.92,0:30:19.14,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.34,0:30:22.39,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}像這樣和別人一起吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.07,0:30:24.53,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.34,0:30:28.73,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}那麼，從今天起這裏就是你的家了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.18,0:30:31.30,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}千萬不要客氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.86,0:30:33.24,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}呃…是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.24,0:30:36.72,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}切！一直「是、是、是、是」地讓人不耐煩
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.18,0:30:40.45,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}你是男孩子吧？乾脆點啦乾脆點
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.32,0:30:42.20,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.91,0:30:43.85,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.30,0:30:48.78,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}去洗個澡，把所有的不愉快統統洗掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.25,0:30:50.92,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}洗澡可是在洗滌生命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.29,0:31:02.29,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}美、美、美、美、美裏小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.74,0:31:03.42,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.99,0:31:09.80,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}啊，它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.93,0:31:12.33,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}是叫做「溫泉企鵝」的一種鳥類
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.02,0:31:22.70,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}還有那樣的鳥存在著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.85,0:31:25.59,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}15 年前可是有許多的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.76,0:31:26.97,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}名字叫「PEN2」
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.14,0:31:30.23,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}是有緣住在這房子裏的另一位同居者呦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.57,0:31:33.43,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}話說回來，不遮下前面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.87,0:31:42.43,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}我鬧得過頭像是做作了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.30,0:31:45.33,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}被看透的人也許是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.06,0:31:48.61,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}葛城 美裏小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.45,0:31:51.91,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}不是壞人…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.62,0:31:54.29,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}洗澡可是在洗滌生命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.04,0:31:59.17,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}不過，洗澡還是會更多地讓我想起一些不愉快的事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.83,0:32:02.65,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}麗的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.61,0:32:07.12,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}您下午不是去過醫院嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.56,0:32:09.51,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}沒有問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.78,0:32:13.16,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}現在的首要事項是重新啟動凍結中的零號機
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.41,0:32:15.07,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}你兒子那樣合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.27,0:32:17.80,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}我覺得他的精神狀態相當不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.19,0:32:19.36,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}隨他去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.60,0:32:23.00,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}不如說這正成了解除零號機凍結的正當借口
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.34,0:32:26.03,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}那麼，就如葛城二佐的提案那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.42,0:32:28.38,screen,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\frz340.9\frx354\fry28\pos(702,380)\bord0\c&H28160C&}小真的房間♡
