Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.90,0:32:42.30,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}沒有任何預備報告
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.30,0:32:45.28,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}突然被選出的第三適格者
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.50,0:32:48.98,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}然後與此相呼應般的使徒來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.20,0:32:52.74,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}同時被強行接收的碇司令的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.50,0:32:55.77,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}整起事件的確很蹊蹺
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.30,0:32:57.09,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.48,0:32:59.73,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}明明打敗了那個使徒…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.73,0:33:03.60,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}但我卻意外的…高興不起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.60,0:33:08.50,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}這也是陌生的天花板啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.79,0:33:10.98,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}這是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.47,0:33:14.62,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}這個城市裏根本就沒有一個我認識的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.88,0:33:16.97,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}這裏可是你的家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.46,0:33:20.17,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}為什麼我會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.82,0:33:36.86,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}真嗣君，我要開門了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.72,0:33:42.97,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}有件事我忘了說
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.37,0:33:46.60,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}你做了一件令人讚賞的、了不起的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.06,0:33:48.14,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}可以挺胸為傲
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.65,0:33:50.31,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}晚安，真嗣君
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.49,0:33:52.42,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.93,0:34:01.38,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}對不起了，轉校生
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.81,0:34:05.87,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}不得不揍你，不揍你難消老子心頭之恨
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.05,0:34:11.89,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}不好意思啊，上次的騷動害他妹妹受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.25,0:34:14.01,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}就是這麼回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.80,0:34:15.88,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.42,0:34:18.47,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}又不是想要駕駛才坐上去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.47,0:34:40.76,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}哪裏是什麼值得被人誇獎的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.91,0:34:43.80,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}就因為說了自己是 EVA 的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.91,0:34:45.41,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}為什麼就要被別人打
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.75,0:34:52.00,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}聽好，真嗣君
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.04,0:34:52.66,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.11,0:34:56.38,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}使徒身上必定有著被稱為「核心」的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.38,0:35:01.89,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}將其破壞是物理性殲滅使徒的唯一手段
