Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.20,0:35:07.22,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}將目標置於中央後，扣下扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.59,0:35:13.55,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}要準確的應對，然後把這感覺融會於全身
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.73,0:35:14.43,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.18,0:35:21.04,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.31,0:35:23.72,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}就這樣以感應瞄準模式繼續練習
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.84,0:35:24.54,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.09,0:35:34.43,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}沒想到還真願意做呢，真嗣君
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.69,0:35:39.57,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}順從別人說的話，那不就是他的處世之道
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.57,0:35:44.13,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}將目標置於中心，扣下扳機…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.14,0:35:47.72,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}將目標置於中心，扣下扳機…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.62,0:35:51.19,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}將目標置於中心，扣下扳機…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.92,0:35:54.57,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}將目標置於中心，扣下扳機…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.69,0:36:01.24,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}說起來，真嗣君轉學第一天就被同學揍了一頓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.38,0:36:03.74,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}駕駛員的安全保障沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.92,0:36:06.57,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}有情報部的監視系統在沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.87,0:36:08.32,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}他也沒受不得了的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.78,0:36:12.69,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}而且，我覺得盡量不要干涉到他的個人生活比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.88,0:36:14.43,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}你們不是住在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.66,0:36:17.11,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}他的「維護」也是你的工作呦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.27,0:36:18.48,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}正因為這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.19,0:36:22.00,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}他比我想像中的還要來得敏感，不好應付
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.23,0:36:23.55,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}已經開始氣餒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.76,0:36:26.47,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}當初不是你自己說大話，要領他回去住的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.47,0:36:27.93,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.70,0:36:33.80,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}也是呢
