Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.63,0:36:42.75,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}知道「豪豬的距離」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.86,0:36:45.59,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}豪豬？那種渾身帶刺的？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.10,0:36:50.57,Default,NTFS,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(50,50)}豪豬雖然想將自己的溫暖傳給對方
